  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb0\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Arrested Reda granted bail",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fort Justice Dilina Gamage today (2) ordered the release of Ranindu Senaratna, who was arrested for protesting against the court order, on bail.",
        "The order was issued today when the suspect was produced at the official residence of the Fort Magistrate.",
        "Yesterday (1) Ranindu Senaratne alias Retta was called for questioning by the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit. While Retta appeared for those investigations, after the investigations he went to the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit and the Colombo Central Zone Crime Investigation Bureau officers arrested him. After giving a statement for about 3 hours at the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit, the officers of the Colombo Central Zone Crime Investigation Bureau who went there at the end of the investigations arrested him.",
        "In this situation, Reta was brought to Kompani Road Police Station premises and the Colombo Central Zone Crime Investigation Bureau officials conducted special investigations.",
        "According to the information of the police, the police later announced that he had been arrested in connection with the incident of protesting against the court order at Fort Bank Mawatha area on May 21."
      ],
